  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Ideal is on a half board basis</p>
<p>Each morning a varied continental breakfast buffet is served, often including pastries, cereals, cold cuts, cheese, seasonal fruit and eggs</p>
<p>A three course evening meal is served each evening with a choice, often including traditional Italian cuisine and local produce</p>
<p>Once a week there is a typical Trentio dinner with local dishes</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
