  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Once you arrive to the Hotel Ideal, you'll be welcomed by the <span class="hps">Cozzini</span> family and their team - the hotel offers cosy rooms, tasty food, a spacious lounge and fantastic wellness area. Each day you can benefit from the daily shuttle service which runs between the lifts, so you can easily start and end your day without worrying about walking too far in ski boots.</span></p>
<h2><span>Hotel ski shuttle</span></h2>
<p><span>The Hotel Ideal is a traditional Italian, family run hotel with a central location in <a data-udi="umb://document/ea59b48ae29b417b81f9c9850d58d038" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ea59b48ae29b417b81f9c9850d58d038}" title="Madonna Di Campiglio" data-anchor="#">Madonna Di Campiglio.</a> The beautiful Brenta Dolomites surround the resort, and getting onto the slopes couldn't be easier with a shuttle service running between the three </span>nearby lifts; <span>Spinale, 5-Laghi and Colarin. The shuttle runs 8:30am - midday and 2:30pm to 5pm.</span></p>
<h2><span>Italian dining</span></h2>
<p><span>When it comes to dinner time, you can expect tasty evening meals with a choice of main. The menu often includes classic Italian dishes, and once a week you can try some of the delicious Trentino cuisine - there is an extensive wine list, so there is bound to be something which pairs nicely with your meal. </span></p>
<p>After a day of adventures, you can enjoy a drink in the lounge-bar, there is also a TV room and a games room for the children.<span></span></p>
<h2><span>Wellness area</span><span></span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel has a lovely spa and wellness area - it is the ideal spot to enjoy a moment of peace. </span></p>
<p><span>Have a dip in the indoor pool with counter current swimming and hydro massage features. Revitalise in the sauna or hammam, or relax with a book in the solarium. </span></p>
<p><span>If you are not worn out, there is also a fitness room with a range of equipment. For a little extra treat, massages and treatments can be booked locally with the masseuses (pay locally).</span></p>
<p> </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Ideal the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
